1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
I leave my book behind

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,800
every Tuesday on purpose.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,500
The café cat is

4
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:13,000
tucked inside the bookmark.

5
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:15,200
The next week,

6
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:19,100
the drawing has a reply.

7
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:21,400
My notes grow

8
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:24,000
longer each visit.

9
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,500
The barista writes:

10
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:32,000
'You're twenty pages ahead of me.'

11
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:34,500
Today, I walk

12
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:36,800
up to the counter.

13
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:40,000
He slides my coffee over.

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,900
A bookmark sits on the saucer,